The BBB Wise Giving Alliance (WGA) is an association of charities formed by a merger of the National Charities Information Bureau (NCIB) and the Council of Better Business Bureaus' Foundation and its Philanthropic Advisory Service (PAS). It publishes a set of standards of accountability for charitable organizations and evaluations of national charities against those standards. Charities that meet the standards are termed "BBB Accredited Charities".
